OL,3,CFor Indians around the world, Air
OL,4,CIndia's legacy makes the tragedy more
OL,5,Cpainful
OL,7,FWritten by Assistant Producer Jeevita
OL,8,FSerrao
OL,10,FThe story of Air India is the story of
OL,11,Fa dream before Indian independence -
OL,12,Fone that became a part of the Indian
OL,13,Fpeople and continues to be so.
OL,15,FWhen business tycoon Jehangir Ratanji
OL,16,FDadabhoy (JRD) Tata qualified as a
OL,17,Fpilot in the 1920s, the Tata group
OL,18,Fdecided to enter the aviation industry
OL,19,Fand establish a global presence for
OL,20,FIndia.
