OL,3,CFor Indians around the world, Air
OL,4,CIndia's legacy makes the tragedy more
OL,5,Cpainful
OL,7,FAir India was a brand built on
OL,8,Fhospitality and unmatched service. The
OL,9,Fever-bowing Maharaja, the mascot of
OL,10,FAir India, became a symbol of that
OL,11,Fservice.
OL,13,FHe was not royalty, but a part of Air
OL,14,FIndia's identity, representing the
OL,15,Fnation's regal nature, showing up in
OL,16,Fcalendars across Indian households, in
OL,17,Fcheeky advertisements and magazines.
