OL,3,CFor Indians around the world, Air
OL,4,CIndia's legacy makes the tragedy more
OL,5,Cpainful
OL,7,FThe airline got its first Boeing in
OL,8,F1960, a Boeing 707 called the Gauri
OL,9,FShankar. This would be the first Air
OL,10,FIndia jet to crash in 1982 after a
OL,11,Fmiscalculation during a severe
OL,12,Frainstorm.
OL,14,FGovernment control meant mismanagement
OL,15,Fand interference in operations, and
OL,16,Fthus began the decline of what was
OL,17,Fonce the nation's pride. Air India
OL,18,Fbegan to incur significant losses, and
OL,19,Fany attempts to privatise the company
OL,20,Fwent in vain.
