OL,3,CFor Indians around the world, Air
OL,4,CIndia's legacy makes the tragedy more
OL,5,Cpainful
OL,7,FAn overhaul was never going to be an
OL,8,Feasy task. In February of 2023, the
OL,9,Fcompany placed an order of 470 jets,
OL,10,Fboth Airbus and Boeing, and announced
OL,11,Fmore international destinations to
OL,12,Fexpand the business.
OL,14,FThis was followed by investing another
OL,15,F#290 million to revamp legacy jets,
OL,16,Fand a further order of 100 jets in
OL,17,FDecember 2024.
