OL,3,CFor Indians around the world, Air
OL,4,CIndia's legacy makes the tragedy more
OL,5,Cpainful
OL,7,FBut what began as an ambition to
OL,8,Frevive the airline's fortunes has now
OL,9,Fbeen met with further disaster. Air
OL,10,FIndia's Boeing 787-8 Dreamliner, bound
OL,11,Ffor London's Gatwick Airport, crashed
OL,12,Fon Thursday, killing over 240 people.
OL,14,FIn a video statement on Thursday after
OL,15,Fthe crash, Air India's chief
OL,16,Fexecutive, Campbell Wilson, said that
OL,17,F"our teams are working around the
OL,18,Fclock to support passengers, crew and
OL,19,Ftheir families as well as
OL,20,Finvestigators however we can."
